<li>Hamerly, Jim, Paquin, Tom and Walton, Susan; <i><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://oreilly.com/catalog/opensources/book/netrev.html">Freeing the Source: The Story of Mozilla</a></i>, in <i>Open Sources: Voices from the Open Source Revolution</i>, O'Reilly, 1999. 280pp, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:BookSources/1565925823" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 1-56592-582-3</a></li>
